#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "संस्थापनम्"

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to obtain &kxstitch;"
msgstr "कथं प्राप्तव्यं &kxstitch;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kxstitch; source can be found at <ulink url=\"http://download.kde.org/"
"stable/kxstitch/\">http://download.kde.org/stable/kxstitch/</ulink>. The "
"&kxstitch; homepage can be found at <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/"
"KXStitch\">http://userbase.kde.org/KXStitch</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"इति &kxstitch; स्रोतः <ulink url=\"http://download.kde.org/stable/kxstitch/"
"\">http://download.kde.org/stable/kxstitch/</ulink> इत्यत्र प्राप्यते । इति "
"&kxstitch; मुखपृष्ठं <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/KXStitch\">http://"
"userbase.kde.org/KXStitch</ulink> इत्यत्र प्राप्यते"

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "आवश्यकताएँ"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kxstitch; has been written with &Qt; 5.x and &kf5-full;."
msgstr "&kxstitch; इत्यनेन सह लिखितम् अस्ति &Qt; ५.x तथा &kf5-पूर्ण;।"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the image import functions the ImageMagick libraries are required, this "
"includes the development headers ImageMagick and Magick++, these are "
"available with your distribution or from <ulink url=\"http://www.imagemagick."
"org/\">http://www.imagemagick.org/</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"इमेज आयातकार्यस्य कृते ImageMagick पुस्तकालयाः आवश्यकाः सन्ति, अस्मिन् विकासशीर्षकाणि "
"ImageMagick तथा Magick++ समाविष्टानि सन्ति, एते भवतः वितरणेन सह अथवा <ulink url="
"\"http://www.imagemagick.org/\">http://www .imagemagick.org/</ulink> इति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compilation and Installation"
msgstr "संकलन तथा स्थापना"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compilation of KXStitch requires cmake and suitable build tools, make, gcc, "
"etc. A build script has been provided which should perform the necessary "
"compilation operations and install KXStitch for which you may be required to "
"enter the root password."
msgstr ""
"KXStitch इत्यस्य संकलनार्थं cmake तथा उपयुक्तानि build tools, make, gcc इत्यादीनां "
"आवश्यकता भवति।एकं build स्क्रिप्ट् प्रदत्ता अस्ति या आवश्यकानि संकलनक्रियाः कर्तुं KXStitch "
"संस्थापयितुं च अर्हति यस्य कृते भवद्भिः मूलगुप्तशब्दं प्रविष्टुं आवश्यकं भवितुम् अर्हति"

#. Tag: screen
#: install.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>bash$</prompt><command>./build.sh</command>"
msgstr "<prompt>bash$</prompt><command>./build.sh</command> इति"
